pageTitle: Itinerary for Sunday, February 10, 2019 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Vancouver, British Columbia

7:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend the 2019 Chinese New Year Celebration Gala, and will deliver remarks.

Floata Seafood Restaurant
180 Keefer Street

Notes for media:

    • Open coverage for remarks
    • Media are asked to arrive to the Keefer Street Entrance no later than 6:30 p.m. and follow directions provided to the media registration.
